long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
A Chrome Extension for our Agents to Book Tickets way faster.
This step skips the time consuming steps while creating a booking.

This extension helps you manage your emails more efficiently by reading data from Gmail and Outlook. It requires permissions to access these services to provide you with the best functionality. We assure you that no data is modified or stored.
